author: to grow
glottocode: No term. Use 'moris'='live' + word to show it is in process

author: to pound, beat
glottocode: pound using end of stick, e.g. corn

author: to fall
glottocode: fall and scatter (of fruit or leaves from tree)

author: feather
glottocode: Usually specify source: e.g. manu fulun=bird feather

author: meat/flesh
glottocode: flesh (of body, fruit...) as opposed to spirit or bones or fat

author: leaf
glottocode: Must be possessed: e.g. ai tahan 'tree leaf'

author: flower
glottocode: Must be possessed: e.g. 'ai funan'='tree flower', sabraka funan=citrus flower

author: fruit
glottocode: Must be possessed: e.g. 'ai fuan'='tree fruit'

author: cloud
glottocode: Not aware of white/rain cloud distinction, but haven't asked.

author: thunder
glottocode: = land bang; Less common: tinan tarutu=year/wet.season+bang
